# 🧠 Habit Tracker App 🌱

Welcome to the **Habit Tracker Web App** — a personal productivity tool designed to help you build and maintain positive habits over time.
Built with ❤️ using **Java**, **Spring Boot**, and **PostgreSQL**.

---

## 🚀 Current Features

- 🔐 **User Authentication**
  - Secure login and registration system
  - Powered by **JWT (JSON Web Tokens)**

---

## 🛠️ Planned Features
- 📅 **Habit Tracking Calendar**
  Visual calendar to mark and view progress on daily habits.

- 🔔 **Reminders & Notifications**
  Get notified to stay on track with your goals!

- 🧩 **Streaks & Achievements**
  Keep up your streaks and earn fun badges for consistency.

- 🎨 **Custom Stickers & Themes**
  Personalize your habit journal with stickers and UI themes.

- 📊 **Progress Analytics**
  Insightful charts and graphs to monitor your progress.

